In Dreams Weird Things Can Happen... Collect... Before...He Gets You.. v0.1.2 Game Story: A Man Who From The World Of The Internet Learns Of Him, The More You Know The More Likely He Will Come... The Man Dreams Of A Tall Thin and very Slender Man. These Dreams Started as curiosity but later changed to his worst nightmare the man seems to think he sees the entity in person and told people that he was gonna try to and get some psychiatric help...Little Did He Know That Would Be HIs Last Dream... The Man Wakes Up In The Place His Dreams Have Taken Place And His Worst Nightmare Becomes Real...